NAME
     sseett - define the user angle of a motor

SYNOPSIS

     sseett mmoottoorr uusseerr__aannggllee

DESCRIPTION

     The sseett macro is used to establish the uusseerr__aannggllee for the motor specified
     by the argument mmoottoorr. It is most often used to set the zero of a motor
     during an alignment procedure.

     The macro uses the built-in function cchhgg__ooffffsseett(()).

EXAMPLE

     sseett tthh 00

